description: Expected results for DataClean multiple indices flow test

expected_messages.description: Start message should be sent successfully
First DataClean message should be sent successfully
Second DataClean message should be sent successfully
Third DataClean message should be sent successfully
End message should be sent successfully

validation_rules.session_consistency: All messages should use the same session ID
validation_rules.message_order: Messages should be sent in the correct order: start -> dataclean(x3) -> end
validation_rules.response_format: DataClean messages should receive no immediate response; End should receive EndAck with Status_Ok
validation_rules.sequence_tracking: All DataClean sequence numbers (0, 1, 2) should be tracked correctly
